pageContext.claim: “You know who got me elected? You know who got me elected? I got me elected. Russia didn't help me at all. Russia, if anything, I think, helped the other side.”
pageContext.analysis: The special counsel's report says that the Russian government perceived it would benefit from a Trump presidency and worked to secure that outcome, while the Trump campaign decided it would benefit from the dissemination of material stolen by the Russian government.
